		"description": "<p>You are always prepared, even when unexpected situations arise. You may temporarily transmute one mundane piece of adventuring gear in your inventory into another, similar mundane piece of adventuring gear that would be useful in the given situation. For example, you may turn a length of rope into the same length of chain, or or a waterskin into a coin pouch. This spell cannot be used on consumable items such as medicinals, poisons, or items such as vials of holy water or acid. The item remains enchanted in this way for 8 hours, after which it reverts back to its original form.</p>\n<p><strong>Cast at Higher Levels:</strong> Increase the spell&rsquo;s duration for 1 hour for every spell slot above 1st.</p>",
